<header class="page-head">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="eyebrow">Pricing</span>
    <h1>Start with the audit.<br>Scale when it proves itself.</h1>
    <p>No lock-in, no platform fees, no seat licenses. You pay for outcomes: a roadmap, a working build, and a team that keeps it running.</p>
  </div>
</header>

<section style="padding-top:10px;">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="tiers">
      <div class="tier reveal">
        <h3>AI Audit</h3>
        <div class="cost">$1,500+</div>
        <div class="per">one-time · 1–2 weeks</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Full workflow analysis</li>
          <li>Staff interviews &amp; shadowing</li>
          <li>Time &amp; cost-loss report</li>
          <li>Prioritized automation roadmap</li>
          <li>ROI estimate per proposed build</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn btn-line">Start here</a>
      </div>
      <div class="tier hot reveal">
        <span class="flag">MOST POPULAR</span>
        <h3>Implementation</h3>
        <div class="cost">$5k–25k</div>
        <div class="per">per project · 2–4 weeks</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Custom agents built for your stack</li>
          <li>CRM, calendar &amp; inbox integration</li>
          <li>Trained on your voice and process</li>
          <li>Tested &amp; deployed to production</li>
          <li>Priced on hours saved, not hours worked</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn btn-glow">Book a scoping call</a>
      </div>
      <div class="tier reveal">
        <h3>Managed Retainer</h3>
        <div class="cost">$1.5k+</div>
        <div class="per">per month · ongoing</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Monitoring &amp; maintenance</li>
          <li>Team training as you hire</li>
          <li>Usage-based costs passed at cost</li>
          <li>New automations every quarter</li>
          <li>Priority support</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn btn-line">Talk to us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="tint">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">The math</span>
      <h2>Why the price is the small number.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="roi reveal">
      <div class="roi-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="big">Manual work compounds. So does removing it.</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p>Take one common example: a team spending 15 hours a week on manual lead follow-up and data entry.</p>
          <div class="math">
            15 hrs/week × $30/hr = <b>$450/week</b><br>
            × 52 weeks = <b>$23,400/year</b><br>
            every year, until it's automated.
          </div>
          <p style="margin-top:18px;">A one-time build that removes that work pays for itself in months — then keeps paying. That's the number we put in front of you at the end of every audit, calculated on your real workflows.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="finale">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="eyebrow reveal">No pressure, real numbers</span>
    <h2 class="reveal">The audit tells you exactly what you'd save — before you commit to anything.</h2>
    <p class="reveal">If the math doesn't work for your business, we'll tell you that too.</p>
    <a href="contact.html" class="btn btn-glow reveal">Book your free audit →</a>
  </div>
</div>

